data.description: 2.7 +/- acres, 3 Bed, 2 Bath, Full Basement Polk County Home and Extra Building Lot. Welcome to your dream home nestled in a serene cul-de-sac location on just under 3 acres! This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and potential. With a spacious master suite, walk-in closet, and an open concept design, this home is designed to meet your modern lifestyle needs.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere with abundant natural light flowing through large windows, illuminating the open-concept living area. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar, making it a delightful space for culinary creations and entertaining guests.    The master suite is a true retreat, offering a private oasis for relaxation. Complete with an ensuite bathroom, you can indulge in a soothing bath or enjoy a refreshing shower after a long day. The walk-in closet provides ample storage space for your wardrobe, keeping everything organized and within reach.    One of the highlights of this property is the full framed and stubbed unfinished basement, presenting endless possibilities for customization. You can transform this space into a recreation room, home gym, or create additional bedrooms and a bath.     Step outside to discover a covered patio, ideal for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply unwinding while enjoying the fresh air. The extra lot, extending over 2.69 acres, provides plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or even future expansion, or a second home site.    Conveniently located with quick access to Highway 27, you'll enjoy easy commuting to Polk and Floyd County, ensuring a seamless connection to nearby amenities, schools, shopping centers, and entertainment options.    Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a home with ample space, endless potential, and a peaceful setting. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities of making this house your forever home!
